plot: This puppet show tells the story of a pacific tribe living in a valley surrounded by mountains. The Aurones were very nature-conscious and earned their living by melting gold to fabricate utensils and tools, unaware of its true value. Tejo, the main character in the series had the power of turning his enemies into fruits, which he had to do ever so frequently with the evil King Grog, who wanted to steal the Aurones' gold from them, and his incompetent gang of Estroles and Gallofa.   Written by  Marta
title: Los Aurones
